In this Minecraft episode we hang out by the castle, setting up some trains, force fields, party golems, and try to figure out where the annoying buzzing sound is coming from.

MindCrack FTB is a modded Minecraft server Guude has setup for the MindCrackers. It is a private (whitelisted) server. We are currently not accepting applications.
